up_lt_up:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⊂ » -/
theorem up_lt_up {s t : set α} : s.up < t.up ↔ «expr ⊂ » s t :=
  iff.rfl
#align up_lt_up up_lt_up
up_le_up:
-- TODO: These lemmas are not tagged `simp` because `set.le_eq_subset` simplifies the LHS
theorem up_le_up {s t : set α} : s.up ≤ t.up ↔ s ⊆ t :=
  iff.rfl
#align up_le_up up_le_up
up_down:
@[simp]
protected theorem up_down (s : SetSemiring α) : s.down.up = s :=
  rfl
#align up_down up_down

down_subset_down:
@[simp]
theorem down_subset_down {s t : SetSemiring α} : s.down ⊆ t.down ↔ s ≤ t :=
  iff.rfl
#align down_subset_down down_subset_down
down_ssubset_down:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⊂ » -/
@[simp]
theorem down_ssubset_down {s t : SetSemiring α} : «expr ⊂ » s.down t.down ↔ s < t :=
  iff.rfl
#align down_ssubset_down down_ssubset_down
